{"type": "article", "id": 25593, "title": "这个设计了不起之今日最佳", "description": "我们尝试推荐一些最近发现的聪明设计。好设计并不只是一种装饰，它还是人们对于生活细节的各种思考，并且综合了包括技术、商业在内的多种力量。我们希望持续关注这些变化，它是美好生活的动力之一。", "date": "2016-04-18T07:08:33Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 1954, "name": "包装"}, {"id": 247, "name": "Nendo"}, {"id": 26348, "name": "Plantui"}, {"id": 26349, "name": "CITCO"}, {"id": 2167, "name": "Zaha Hadid"}, {"id": 26350, "name": "Rashmeet Saggu"}, {"id": 26351, "name": "Denis Santachiara"}, {"id": 26352, "name": "Nastya Lukina"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 30, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607130040XzwIfomYMxGeAW8O.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p>\n<h2>Tangle side table by Nendo </h2>\n<p>这是 Nendo 为意大利品牌 Capellini 设计的白色边桌，是用铁做的，一共三种型号。中间型号的桌子是最基本的形状，另外两张桌子都带有一根螺旋形状的弯曲桌腿，使桌子之间构成环环相扣的状态。可以沿着桌腿将另一张桌子旋转出来，当不需要使用时又收回去。螺旋形的设计并不复杂，倒是给人一种奇妙的趣味。<a href=\"http://www.nendo.jp/en/works/tangle-table-3/?erelease\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181845HfOkJzC0FPh8VUpI.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70731707\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181845punsLHE4cdxaSljJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181846IOTo10vr6V3aeniX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181846OYtmx4s9cEKgBNWb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181847q3upeS1cKRJlzAZt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181847rmBeL9qsfgGICEzV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.89209402\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: normal;\">Smart Garden by Plantui</span></h2>\n<p>芬兰的团队 Plantui 开发了一种“智能花园”，绿色植物夹在一个被打开的圆球中间，就像一个胶囊。植物的生长不需要土壤或肥料，通过圆球上面内置的 LED 灯提供光合作用，底部的水泵则调节灌溉频率，非常方便。可以种植白菜、辣椒等蔬菜，从种子到成熟需要 5 到 8 周时间。Plantui 目前推出了三款产品，其中 Plantui6 获得了去年的红点奖。售价 99 欧元起，<a href=\"http://plantui.com/smart-gardens/plantui-6/\">这里是购买链接。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181848Zhay0eMRwvPizGm3.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.43\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181848sWuZnoNSfX6kmhpw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.45205479\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181848jC4m6zrGignJVWEc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181849mcStUEfLjanY4BZv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75059952\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181849fTi9jIULJog3FZWm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75136612\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181850eG5Px0WDEfKwv2Ni.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>The Chemistry lamps by Rashmeet Saggu</h2>\n<p>这是一盏有实验风格的灯，来自印度刚毕业不久的设计师 Rashmeet Saggu。其中一盏灯就像是利用实验时常用的圆锥瓶改造的，瓶口接上了灯，瓶子作为玻璃灯泡使用，留在瓶子上的白色刻度提醒了人们它从前的用途，有旧物利用的质朴和原始。另一种灯保留了圆锥形的形状，更明亮。连接灯泡的线绕了一个圈，可以直接挂在墙上。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071818501tfYh7noT8M5u0Qv.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181851wRXYVhaLn0irpGvU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75047619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181851N2AqFBID49OPEpUd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75047619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181852qZhlQoiCIa6gDUnp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75047619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181852RMjTsFPKh8XYxO4Z.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.65904762\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>“valle”by Zaha Hadid &amp;CITCO</h2>\n<p>这是扎哈和意大利石材公司 CITCO 合作的书架，使用了黑色花岗岩做成 4 个型号不同的模块。每一块可以看做是一个线条，从中间向左右或上面的墙面延伸，拥有扎哈所特有的流动的曲线。这种流动性体现出的轻盈与厚重的花岗岩构成对比，很有艺术感。4 个模块的架子可以任意搭配在一起，这个系列与扎哈产品设计的风格是类似的，<a href=\"http://www.citco.it/en/zaha-hadid\">点击这里</a>可查看她与  CITCO 合作的产品设计。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181853pW4UR1PqMz3IFcQm.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71271394\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181853ubFHq3RghsMx5pCd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181854BG3gfyKvwm8bNlLt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70660147\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181854eiv20mdso3b7yUG1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75061125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181855IH4DgZE57m0Ypstj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67114914\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Ca.Mia by Denis Santachiara</h2>\n<p>这是一张充气床，是意大利设计师 Denis Santachiara 为意大利家具商 Campeggi 设计的。充气前可以完全收纳在一个布袋里，充气的部分是床垫，可以拉出蚊帐作为遮盖。小房子一样的形状给予了更多安稳和温馨，这样那些临时过夜的人可以不用睡袋或者沙发了。<a href=\"http://www.campeggisrl.it/it/prodotti/camia\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181855G40nOkj2hrF9IEum.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181856p2qYo0EL6uRmzKGJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.47\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071818560BvIyNWKDFmkb4aZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.51666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181857VYHOE6puXD1CNPRK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181857FTahH7J3Lp4XKAxl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.53425926\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: normal;\">Inizio olive oil design concept by Nastya Lukina &amp; Максим Петров</span></h2>\n<p>这瓶橄榄油包装可以从外形上看到橄榄的特征，或者可以看做是一滴油。瓶口的盖子微有倾斜，透过玻璃瓶能衬出里面青绿色，强调了天然的概念。关于橄榄油的信息集中在中间的水滴一样的黑色卡纸上，很简洁。在外面的包装时则恰好将卡纸部分露出来，可以简练而巧妙地表现出信息。设计者来自莫斯科，它目前还是一个概念。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181857SsCDebYTmRa3n8tU.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181858HJ0kF5isDgXLyOev.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071818583gFY0OfrzUpJ8LwZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181859CbeIgp8xdW9RmQKi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071818594FbaxuRrhplZ07cA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}